modName: RaceMenu Preset - Yennefer of Vengerberg - The Witcher
summary: The Witcher 3 - Yennefer of Vengerberg RaceMenu Preset.
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://www.bhmpics.com/wallpapers/yennefer_of_vengerberg_the_witcher_3__wild_hunt-1920x1080.jpg[/img]
[center][b][color=#674ea7][size=5]Yennefer Of Vengerberg

[/size][/color][/b][size=3]I'm a huge fan of the Witcher series, and I want to share with you this RaceMenu preset.

It adds the beautiful Yennefer of Vengerberg to your RaceMenu.

With RaceMenu I think, I was able to get pretty close how Yennefer really looks, I hope you will enjoy this Preset!

Base Race: Breton[/size]
